doctors in the speciality 
dont bother lee goldsmith a physician and practicing 
lawyer says to those thinking of cosmetic surgery its an 
abused unnecessary procedure 
goldsmith only sees the failures in his new yorkarea law 
practice such as the a woman who came in after an implant with 
one breast going up and one going down and the surgeon was going 
to charge her to do it over 
but successes outnumber horror stories in the 
multibilliondollar industry an estimated 1 million to 3 million 
image enhancement procedures a year in the united states 
cher had her nose refined several years ago it looked too 
big onscreen and bothered me hey if i need cosmetic surgery the 
