i wrote my mother and told her dont recommend to nobody to 
come illegally to the united states hernandez said 
mcnarys crackdown is an effort to prevent a repeat of late 1988 
and early 1989 when more than 50000 central americans streamed 
across the border to apply for political asylum in south texas 
the ins had allowed asylumseekers to travel to their families 
in the united states but officials in cities with large central 
american populations such as miami and los angeles complained 
