power to the moslems 
aoun rejects the plan because it does not provide for a complete 
withdrawal by syrias 40000 troops who have been in lebanon since 
1976 under an arab league peacekeeping mandate those forces 
control most of the country 
geagea has taken no public stand on the latest peace accord but 
recognizes hrawi 
