to appear immediately for drug and alcohol tests after the crash 
drug tests taken 44 hours after the crash showed no trace of 
illegal substances in either man 
the safety board examines all aviation crashes determines their 
probable cause and makes recommendations to airlines 
manufacturers congress and the faa for improving safety the board 
has no regulatory power 
