information at certain points at a minimum the media argued they 
should have an opportunity to inspect and copy the videotape and 
any written transcript as soon as possible after the proceeding 
meanwhile greene must rule on whether the approximately 150 
classified documents in dispute are necessary for poindexter to get 
a fair trial if he rules that they are necessary and if us 
intelligence agencies refuse to allow their declassification the 
poindexter case could be in jeopardy 
