the offer monday calling it an affront to this court 
the judge said dropping the fines would send the wrong message 
to the community and to future strikers 
mcglothlin said it would convince people that mass 
violations of the law are a valid means of conducting a strike 
he said he knew dropping the fines would make all parties in the 
dispute happy miners would be able to get back to work state and 
